tingDetails\">{{cite web|url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12245833|title=Announcement on Amazon producing the Lord of the Rings TV show in NZ is 'imminent'|last=Walls|first=Jason|work=[[New Zealand Herald]]|date=July 2, 2019|access-date=August 24, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808001508/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12245833|archive-date=August 8, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NZFilmingJul2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/113918245/nz-nearly-lost-amazons-lord-of-the-rings-production-after-christchurch-attacks|title=NZ nearly lost Amazon's Lord of the Rings production after Christchurch attacks|website=[[Stuff.co.nz]]|date=July 2, 2019|access-date=August 24, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824040320/https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/113918245/nz-nearly-lost-amazons-lord-of-the-rings-production-after-christchurch-attacks|archive-date=August 24, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NZFilmingJun2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.newstalkzb.co.nz/news/entertainment/new-zealand-set-to-be-location-for-lord-of-the-rings-1-5-billion-tv-show/|title=New $1.5b LOTR TV series set to film in Auckland|work=[[Newstalk ZB]]|date=June 30, 2019|access-date=April 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630140349/https://www.newstalkzb.co.nz/news/entertainment/new-zealand-set-to-be-location-for-lord-of-the-rings-1-5-billion-tv-show/|archive-date=June 30, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NZFilmingSep2019\">{{cite web|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/tv-radio/115878784/amazons-lord-of-the-rings-tv-series-to-start-filming-in-auckland|title=Amazon's The Lord of The Rings TV series to start filming in Auckland|last=Te|first=Mandy|website=[[Stuff.co.nz]]|date=September 18, 2019|access-date=April 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918062317/https://www.stuff.co.nz/enterta