b-weiss-1202663930/|title=Netflix Wins Overall Film, TV Deal For \u2018Game Of Thrones\u2019 Creators David Benioff & D.B. Weiss|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=August 7, 2019|access-date=April 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807232300/https://deadline.com/2019/08/game-of-thrones-creators-netflix-overall-deal-david-benioff-d-b-weiss-1202663930/|archive-date=August 7, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CreativeTeamVideo\">{{cite tweet|number=1155142047420080129|user=LOTRonPrime|title=Meet our Fellowship|date=July 27, 2019|access-date=July 28, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902014625/https://twitter.com/lotronprime/status/1155142047420080129|archive-date=September 2, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CreativeTeamDeadline\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/amazon-creative-team-lord-of-the-rings-1202655353/|title=Amazon Sets Creative Team For \u2018Lord Of The Rings\u2019 TV Series Including \u2018GoT\u2019 & \u2018Breaking Bad\u2019 Producers \u2013 TCA|last=White|first=Peter|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=July 27, 2019|access-date=April 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727162003/https://deadline.com/2019/07/amazon-creative-team-lord-of-the-rings-1202655353/|archive-date=July 27, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NoShippey\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cbr.com/report-tom-shippey-out-at-amazon-lord-of-the-rings/|title=Report: Amazon's Lord of the Rings Parts Ways With Tolkien Scholar Tom Shippey|last=Jennings|first=Collier|website=[[Comic Book Resources]]|date=April 16, 2020|access-date=April 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423135800/https://www.cbr.com/report-tom-shippey-out-at-amazon-lord-of-the-rings/|archive-date=April 23, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KavenaghVariety\">{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/lord-of-the-rings-series-amazon-cast-markella-kavenagh-1203268175/|title='Lord of the 